{"data":[{"name":"84:1","price":"1. Als de hemel splijt,","arabic":"إِذَا ٱلسَّمَآءُ ٱنشَقَّتۡ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5885,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"84:2","price":"2. En het (de hemel) naar zijn Heer luistert en Hem gehoorzaamt, en zijn plicht nakomt.","arabic":"وَأَذِنَتۡ لِرَبِّهَا وَحُقَّتۡ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5886,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"84:3","price":"3. En als de aarde uitgestrekt wordt.","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡأَرۡضُ مُدَّتۡ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5887,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"84:4","price":"4. En alles uitgeworpen heeft wat zij in zich heeft, en ledig wordt.","arabic":"وَأَلۡقَتۡ مَا فِيهَا وَتَخَلَّتۡ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5888,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"84:5","price":"5. En het (de aarde) naar haar Heer luistert en Hem gehoorzaamt, en haar plicht nakomt.","arabic":"وَأَذِنَتۡ لِرَبِّهَا وَحُقَّتۡ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5889,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"84:6","price":"6. O mens waarlijk, jullie keren naar jullie Heer terug – met jullie daden en handelingen (goed en slecht), een zekere terugkeer.","arabic":"يَٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ إِنَّكَ كَادِحٌ إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ كَدۡحٗا فَمُلَٰقِيهِ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5890,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"84:7","price":"7. Dan, zal er voor hem die de afrekening in zijn rechterhand krijgt.","arabic":"فَأَمَّا مَنۡ أُوتِيَ كِتَٰبَهُۥ بِيَمِينِهِۦ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5891,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"84:8","price":"8. Hij zal zeker een gemakkelijke afrekening krijgen.","arabic":"فَسَوۡفَ يُحَاسَبُ حِسَابٗا يَسِيرٗا","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5892,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"84:9","price":"9. En zal blijmoedig tot zijn familie terugkeren!","arabic":"وَيَنقَلِبُ إِلَىٰٓ أَهۡلِهِۦ مَسۡرُورٗا","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5893,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"84:10","price":"10. Maar iedereen die zijn afrekening achter zijn rug krijgt.","arabic":"وَأَمَّا مَنۡ أُوتِيَ كِتَٰبَهُۥ وَرَآءَ ظَهۡرِهِۦ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5894,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"84:11","price":"11. Hij zal zijn vernietiging over zich uitroepen.","arabic":"فَسَوۡفَ يَدۡعُواْ ثُبُورٗا","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5895,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"84:12","price":"12. Hij zal braden in een laaiend vuur.","arabic":"وَيَصۡلَىٰ سَعِيرًا","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5896,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"84:13","price":"13. Waarlijk, hij was blijmoedig bij zijn familie!","arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ كَانَ فِيٓ أَهۡلِهِۦ مَسۡرُورًا","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5897,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"84:14","price":"14. Waarlijk, hij dacht dat hij nooit (tot Ons) zou terugkeren!","arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ ظَنَّ أَن لَّن يَحُورَ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5898,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"84:15","price":"15. Ja, waarlijk zijn Heer is alwetend over hem.","arabic":"بَلَىٰٓۚ إِنَّ رَبَّهُۥ كَانَ بِهِۦ بَصِيرٗا","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5899,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"84:16","price":"16. Dus Ik zweer bij de rode gloed van de zonsondergang.","arabic":"فَلَآ أُقۡسِمُ بِٱلشَّفَقِ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5900,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"84:17","price":"17. En bij de nacht en alles wat het in zijn duisternis verzamelt.","arabic":"وَٱلَّيۡلِ وَمَا وَسَقَ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5901,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"84:18","price":"18. En bij de maan, als die vol is.","arabic":"وَٱلۡقَمَرِ إِذَا ٱتَّسَقَ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5902,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"84:19","price":"19. Jullie zullen je zeker van stadium tot stadium voortbewegen.","arabic":"لَتَرۡكَبُنَّ طَبَقًا عَن طَبَقٖ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5903,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"84:20","price":"20. Wat scheelt hen toch, dat zij niet geloven?","arabic":"فَمَا لَهُمۡ لَا يُؤۡمِنُونَ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5904,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"84:21","price":"21. En als de Koran voor hen gereciteerd wordt, dat zij niet neerknielen?","arabic":"وَإِذَا قُرِئَ عَلَيۡهِمُ ٱلۡقُرۡءَانُ لَا يَسۡجُدُونَۤ۩","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5905,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"84:22","price":"22. Nee, (in tegendeel) degenen die niet geloven, verloochenen.","arabic":"بَلِ ٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُواْ يُكَذِّبُونَ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5906,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"84:23","price":"23. En Allah weet het het beste wat zij in zich hebben.","arabic":"وَٱللَّهُ أَعۡلَمُ بِمَا يُوعُونَ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5907,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"84:24","price":"24. Verkondig dus aan hen een pijnlijke bestraffing.","arabic":"فَبَشِّرۡهُم بِعَذَابٍ أَلِيمٍ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5908,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"84:25","price":"25. Behalve degenen die geloven en goede daden verrichten, voor hen is er een beloning welke nooit zal eindigen.","arabic":"إِلَّا ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُواْ وَعَمِلُواْ ٱلصَّٰلِحَٰتِ لَهُمۡ أَجۡرٌ غَيۡرُ مَمۡنُونِۭ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5909,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"}],"chapter":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq","Chapter Al-Inshiqaq","Inshiqaq","Surah Inshiqaq","Chapter Inshiqaq","Al Inshiqaq","Surah Al Inshiqaq","Chapter Al Inshiqaq","Surah 84","Chapter 84","The Splitting Open","الإنشقاق"]}